        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，FleetManagement作为中心节点。那它和仓库是什么关系？是创建关系还是管理关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是创建关系，FleetManagement可以创建仓库实例。另外它还能启动库存监控，这个关系叫Starts，指向Logistics_StockLevel。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Starts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上Creates到Warehouse，以及Starts到StockLevel。还有别的核心操作吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FleetManagement还需要能上报库存异常，这个Reports关系也指向StockLevel，但和Starts是不同场景。一个是启动监控，一个是异常上报。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reports",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，Reports和Starts都指向StockLevel，语义区分我理解了。那仓库本身有什么行为？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "仓库可以接收配送路线，Receives关系指向Logistics_DeliveryRoute。同时FleetManagement也能对配送路线发表评论，Comments on关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Receives",
        "Comments on"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，Warehouse Receives DeliveryRoute，以及User Comments on DeliveryRoute。配送路线还有什么属性？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "配送路线有两个关键状态：可以被接受Accepted，也可以被上报Reported。分别关联到Warehouse和StockLevel。",
      "elements_involved": [
